snippet.title: Cotton (ARCADE)
snippet.description:
An unusual side shooter from Sega back in the day. It has comic relief in each stage as
a witch and fairy team up to save Fairyland
I believe this game came out for the now dead, TurboGrafx 16

Side note, game actually ends before the video, I was trying to do the "extra" stage, but, there was no difference,s...(fart sounds)
